jq --arg buildroot "$FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR" --argjson data '{"git+ssh://git@github.com/jonathon-love/dialogs.git#cb8c36eae8f651db6116a511d8416c87c7251d52": "flatpak-node/git-packages/dialogs-cb8c36eae8f651db6116a511d8416c87c7251d52#cb8c36eae8f651db6116a511d8416c87c7251d52", "ssh://git@github.com/jonathon-love/dialogs.git#cb8c36eae8f651db6116a511d8416c87c7251d52": "flatpak-node/git-packages/dialogs-cb8c36eae8f651db6116a511d8416c87c7251d52#cb8c36eae8f651db6116a511d8416c87c7251d52"}' 'walk(    if type == "object" and (.version | type == "string") and $data[.version]    then        .version = "git+file:\($buildroot)/\($data[.version])"    else .    end)' $FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR/package-lock.json > $FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR/package-lock.json.new
